Class-DBI-Loader-Oracle version 0.02
====================================

This module provides an Oracle driver for Class::DBI::Loader.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

The tests require an Oracle server. While this module supports
many different ways of configuring a connection, setting the
following environment variables should ensure successful tests:

    ORACLE_HOME    - path to version of Oracle used to compile DBD::Oracle
    ORACLE_USERID  - user/pass@sid

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

    Class::DBI::Loader
    Class::DBI::Oracle
    DBD::Oracle

